data.actual_result: Group DM invite embeds display the group's icon as a circle
data.expected_result: Group DM invite embeds should display the group's icon as a square like with server invite embeds
data.short_description: Group DM invite embeds display the icon as a circle rather than a square
data.steps_to_repro: - Create a Group DM - Open the Add Friends to DM modal and copy the invite - Paste it into the DM and observe the icon (And no, the default icon is not just circular shaped, you can upload a new one to further check)
